<!-- ======= Values Section ======= -->
<section class="values" id="values">
<div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
<div class="row justify-content-around gy-4">
<div class="col-lg-6 img-bg" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="100" style="background-image: url(assets/img/values.png)"></div>
<div class="col-lg-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
<h3>Values</h3>
<div class="icon-box d-flex position-relative" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
<i class="bi bi-easel flex-shrink-0"></i>
<div>
<h4>
<a class="stretched-link" href="">Integrity</a>
</h4>
<p style="text-align: justify">
                    At Jalenso Holdings, integrity is the foundation of everything we do. We maintain the highest ethical
standards and are committed to transparency and honesty in all interactions with clients, partners,
employees and communities. Our decisions and actions are guided by a strong moral compass,
ensuring that every project is delivered with honesty and accountability. We believe that trust is
earned through consistent, ethical conduct, and we work diligently to uphold this trust in every
engagement.
                  </p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- End Icon Box -->
<div class="icon-box d-flex position-relative" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
<i class="bi bi-patch-check flex-shrink-0"></i>
<div>
<h4>
<a class="stretched-link" href="">Innovation</a>
</h4>
<p style="text-align: justify">
                    We embrace a culture of continuous innovation, pushing the boundaries of traditional engineering
and construction practices. Jalenso Holdings remains committed to adopting the latest technologies,
sustainable materials and creative methodologies to improve project outcomes. By fostering an
environment where new ideas thrive, we encourage our teams to explore cutting-edge solutions that
drive efficiency, reduce environmental impact and enhance community benefits. Our dedication to
innovation ensures that we remain at the forefront of industry advancements, setting benchmarks in
quality and performance.
                  </p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- End Icon Box -->
<div class="icon-box d-flex position-relative" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
<i class="bi bi-brightness-high flex-shrink-0"></i>
<div>
<h4>
<a class="stretched-link" href="">Safety Excellence</a>
</h4>
<p style="text-align: justify">
                   The well-being of our employees, clients and the public is paramount. Jalenso Holdings is dedicated
to maintaining the highest standards of safety across all our operations, adhering to South African
National Standards and international best practices. We implement rigorous safety training
programmes, continuously update our safety protocols and invest in advanced protective measures
to mitigate risks. Our proactive approach to health and safety ensures that every project is executed
with utmost care, reinforcing our commitment to zero harm and fostering a culture where safety is
everyone’s responsibility.
                  </p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- End Icon Box -->
<div class="icon-box d-flex position-relative" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
<i class="bi bi-geo-alt flex-shrink-0"></i>
<div>
<h4>
<a class="stretched-link" href="">Sustainability &amp; Social Responsibility</a>
</h4>
<p style="text-align: justify">
                    We recognise that our success is intertwined with the health of our environment and the prosperity of
the communities in which we operate. Jalenso Holdings is committed to sustainable practices that
minimise environmental impact, including the use of eco-friendly materials, energy-efficient designs
and waste reduction strategies. We prioritise social responsibility by supporting local economies,
investing in skills development and ensuring that our projects contribute positively to society. By
integrating environmental stewardship and community upliftment into our operations, we strive to
create enduring value that benefits both current and future generations.
                  </p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- End Icon Box -->
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Values Section -->
<!-- ======= Services Section ======= -->
<section class="services section-bg" id="services">
<div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
<div class="section-header">
<h2>Our Services</h2>
</div>
<div class="row gy-4">
<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
<div class="service-item position-relative">
<div class="icon">
<i class="fa-solid fa-mountain-city"></i>
</div>
<h3>Rubber Lining &amp; Corrosion Protection </h3>
<p style="text-align: justify">
                 Surface preparation to SA 2.5 standards (ISO 8501‑1), followed by application of
rubber linings (natural, hard rubber, bromobutyl) for tanks, chutes and pipelines,
and protective coatings per ISO/SANS 12944 for harsh environments. This protects
assets from acids, alkalis, brines, slurry and environmental degradation.
                  <br/>
</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- End Service Item -->
<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
<div class="service-item position-relative">
<div class="icon">
<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-from-ground-water"></i>
</div>
<h3>CIVIL WORKS (DESIGN, BUILD &amp; MAINTAIN)</h3>
<p style="text-align: justify">
                 Comprehensive earthworks, concrete foundations, slabs, bund walls, platforms,
roads and drainage systems, executed in accordance with SANS 2001 and SANS
10100 standards. This service includes detailed design, construction and
maintenance of industrial and mining civils.
                </p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- End Service Item -->
<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
<div class="service-item position-relative">
<div class="icon">
<i class="fa-solid fa-compass-drafting"></i>
</div>
<h3>ELECTRICAL WORKS &amp; CABLE RACK SYSTEMS</h3>
<p style="text-align: justify">
                  Installation of low‑voltage distribution boards, cable ladders, trays and trunking,
earthing networks and instrumentation in compliance with SANS 10142‑1 and IEC
61537. This service encompasses cable routing, segregation, thermal management
and commissioning, ensuring safe and reliable electrical infrastructure.
                </p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- End Service Item -->
<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
<div class="service-item position-relative">
<div class="icon">
<i class="fa-solid fa-person-digging"></i>
</div>
<h3>STRUCTURAL STEEL FABRICATION &amp; WELDING</h3>
<p style="text-align: justify">
                  Design, fabrication and assembly of structural steelwork, handrails, gratings,
platforms and modular skids, adhering to AWS D1.1 and SANS 10162‑1. Services
include shop detailing, welding, trial assembly, galvanizing (SANS 121) and on‑site
erection, delivering robust and compliant steel structures.
                </p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- <div
              class="col-lg-4 col-md-6"
              data-aos="fade-up"
              data-aos-delay="400"
            >
              <div class="service-item position-relative">
                <div class="icon">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-pen-ruler"></i>
                </div>
